name: OSINT-Tools
description: The OSINT Framework is a powerful collection of tools and methods designed for open-source intelligence gathering. This framework covers a wide range of categories to help security researchers, investigators, and analysts uncover crucial information effectively.

name: Social-Engineering-Tools
description: A powerful collection of tools designed for social engineering research, penetration testing, and security awareness training. These tools help security researchers understand human manipulation tactics and improve defense mechanisms.
